#CAMERA 3
#phrase Hero 1
With each hired mercenary, there is a 33% chance of a collector appearing in your group, which brings loot from the corpses of slain enemies.
#CAMERA 3
#phrase Hero 2
By hiring 3 mercenaries, a collector will join your group with a 99% probability.